H_LogEntryInTermImpliesSafeAtTermCandidateAppendEntries == 
    \A t \in Server : 
    \A m \in appendEntriesRequestMsgs :
        (/\ m.mtype = AppendEntriesRequest
         /\ m.mentries # <<>>
        \*  /\ m.mentries[1] = currentTerm[t]
